---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
    <div class="bg-gray-950 py-20">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 prose prose-invert">
            <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">Terms of Service</h1>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Last updated: July 2026</p>

            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-10">1. Services</h2>
            <p>RigRescue provides remote computer repair, tech consulting, and local in-person services in the Deltona, FL area.</p>

            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-10">2. Diagnostic Fee</h2>
            <p>A $50 diagnostic fee is charged upfront and is credited toward any paid repair work you authorize.</p>

            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-10">3. Payments & Quotes</h2>
            <p>No repair work begins until you review and approve the quote. All payments are processed securely through Stripe.</p>

            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-10">4. Limitation of Liability</h2>
            <p>We are not liable for data loss. We strongly recommend you back up important data before any repair.</p>

            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-10">5. Governing Law</h2>
            <p>These terms are governed by the laws of the State of Florida.</p>

            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-10">Contact Us</h2>
            <p>Email: support@rigrescue.net</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</Layout>
